text.tspan: To help you summarize and analyze your argumentative texts, your articles, your scientific texts, your history texts as well as your well-
structured analyses work of art, we provides you with a "Summary and category text tool" : an educational tool that identifies and summarizes
the important ideas and facts of your documents then give you the category of that text. Summarize in 1-Click, go to the main idea or skim
through so that you can then interpret your texts quickly and develop your syntheses.
